data.description: Embrace the charm of this two-story, 4-bedroom, 2 1/2-bathroom in Lakes By the Bay community. Just moments from Black Point Marina and the convenience of the turnpike. This residence boasts a seamless transition from its spacious living room to the inviting dining area—an entertainer's delight. The kitchen features granite countertops, while every window has the stylish zebra blinds and equipped with hurricane accordion shutters. The blend of tile on the first floor and the warmth of wood and wood laminate flooring on the stairs and second story. A spacious backyard, a canvas for your personal oasis with ample space for a potential pool.
